&lt;li&gt;Facilitate training for warehouse associates on operational SOPs to improve inventory related metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan physical inventory events including planning, execution, and reconciliation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve inventory-related processes and collaborate with department leaders to enhance KPI performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure safety, food-safety, and compliance standards are upheld at all times&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate performance results and systemic issues to leadership with clear documentation and recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
